title: Tech to wrap home stand up Tuesday with East Carolina - VT hokiesports.com
content: Tech to wrap home stand up Tuesday with East Carolina  VT hokiesports.com
description: Off to its best program start since 2013, the Virginia Tech baseball team (9-1) will wrap up its 11-game, season-opening home stand on Tuesday, March 8, when Tech competes in a midweek showdown against East Carolina (6-5).
